⊕meta⊕
name = "review"
description = "Read-only code review of a branch against main. Fire via: sky emit pr.opened"
trigger.sky_event.event = "pr.opened"
⊕⊕

※※
Run a high-signal code review when a PR is opened.
The review node diffs against review.base (default: main), loads CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md
scoped to the changed files, and sends everything to Claude with the built-in review prompt.
No files are written — the node denies all write tools automatically.
Use {{pr.head_ref}} to pass the branch name from the webhook payload.
※※

§review§
review.base = "main"
review.target = "{{pr.head_ref}}"
model = "sonnet"
§§
